{"tid":1532100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"橫琴揭走私美金到澳門　截3車涉款172.5萬美元","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:00:20.000Z","uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f56c69189d00cc1eb2b8538a0333fa3fff73e42a","tid":1532100,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"橫琴口岸接連查獲走私美元到澳門案件。拱北海關轄下的橫琴海關聯同橫琴緝私分局查獲3輛私家車，搜出共172.5萬美元，折合約1352萬港元。<br />\n拱北海關指，涉案車輛經橫琴口岸小客車通道出境到澳門，關員在車上同一位置的暗格，分別發現藏有50多萬至60萬的懷疑走私美元。案件正進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【戰略】撳美金現金係最低成本嘅革命手段，成功嘅話無需攬炒，得中共自炒。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/adjxzfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/adjxzfU</a>"},{"pid":"fe42cff3c6c0ae63642e7c617cb7b71eb6cd5fb7","tid":1532100,"uid":50328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cba6e2e8ffa2a6be5be62e85b1ee1a4a24c2f5b","tid":1532100,"uid":136958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"正呀喂 回血劍咁樣玩法"},{"pid":"c3d6aa68ec64156e6481607961b9ad79f555e36b","tid":1532100,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:01:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"807d7091967958d633e33bebf23347d3d1bb7bec","tid":1532100,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:02:52.000Z","msg":"去澳門大學拋過去算啦, 得條鐵絲網隔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb8c47339534bf6c178661e7752ffa048a40dd3","tid":1532100,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:0